    <h2>PRIVATE vs COMMERCIAL Projects.</h2>
    <p>Private projects, like projects (mixing, mastering, production) 
      for Client's albums, singles, etc. 
      to be posted on Music Distributors can be ordered through
      the commission form.
    Commercial projects, like advertisements,
      synchronization work (video game soundtracks, film soundtracks, etc.)
    need to be disclosed in emails and cannot be ordered through the commission form.<br /><br /></p>
    

