    <h2>REVISIONS.</h2>
    <p>
      Client will get two Revisions.
      What IS covered by a revision: You’d like the volume
      of an instrument and/or vocal adjusted. You’d like effects adjusted (i.e.
      more reverb, less delay) What is NOT covered by a revision: Does
      not include arrangement changes: Things like creating drops, stop effects
      and mutes.
      As I work, I will send updates in .mp3, this is the best time for feedback!
      Any extra revisions will cost an extra fee.
    </p>

